Name: PhysicalStructureSchemeName
Description: A name for the PhysicalStructureScheme. May be expressed in multiple languages. Repeat the element to express names with different content, for example different names for different systems.

Name: Label
Description: A display label for the PhysicalStructureScheme. May be expressed in multiple languages. Repeat for labels with different content, for example, labels with differing length limitations.

Name: Description
Description: A description of the PhysicalStructureScheme. May be expressed in multiple languages and supports the use of structured content.

Name: PhysicalStructureSchemeReference
Description: Reference to an existing PhysicalStructureScheme for inclusion.

Name: PhysicalStructureReference
Description: A PhysicalStructure description providing the primary link to the LogicalRecord and general structural information. Each description can apply to one or more data files containing the same logical records in the same overall structure.

Name: PhysicalStructureGroupReference
Description: A group of PhysicalStructure descriptions for administrative or conceptual purposes.
